* Concepts

** Process Priority (NICE value)
   
this is the a number that is applied to a process to gauage it's importance to the system

ranges from 20 - -19

only root is allowed to nice a value below 0


** Process States
T - Stopped
R - Runnable (ready)
R - Running (user)
R - Running (kernel)
K - Sleeping
D - Sleeping
S - Sleeping
Z - Zombie

